":3},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Parenting: Be gentle with your children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Ghazali reported: A man came to Abdullah ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, and he complained about disrespect from his son. Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cHave you supplicated against him?\u201d The man said yes. Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cYou have corrupted him.\u201d Al-Ghazali said, \"It is recommended to be gentle\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20775,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/25\/sufyan-know-your-self\/","url_meta":{"origin":21957,"position":4},"title":"Sufyan on Confidence: If you know your self, you will not be harmed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Mubarak reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you know yourself, you will not be harmed by whatever is said about you.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 6\/390 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0641\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0636\u064f\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e 6\/390 \u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33311,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/28\/ibn-mubarak-best-provisions\/","url_meta":{"origin":21957,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Blessings: Best things a human being is given from Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Habib al-Jallab reported: I asked Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cWhat is the best thing a human being can be given?\u201d He said, \u201cInnate intelligence.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat if it is not so?\u201d He said, \u201cGood manners.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat if it is not so?\u201d He said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/21957","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=21957"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/21957\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"hr